t_news_breaking_video::clip_card_2::goal: Waraabbii tokko keessatti waan ta'e qaaccessi.
t_news_breaking_video::text_card_0::text: Gabaasi Suur-sagalee oduu tasaa seenessa waan ta'aa jiru ibsu, qabxiilee ijoo qaaccessuu, qaamota ijoo, fi odeeffannoo hamma ammaatti baraman kamiinuu kan barbaaduudha. Gabaasaan maal akka lafarratti mul'atu bakka oduchi itti ta'e. Waraabbiiwwan haqa bu'uuraa fi yoo danda'ame gaafannoo namoota ragaa ta'anii wajjin goote agarsiisi.
t_news_breaking_video::ms_moreinfo::head: Itti aanee
t_news_breaking_video::title: Gabaasa Suur-sagalee Oduu Tasaa
t_news_breaking_video::clip_card_0::goal: Bakkasaa Agarsiisi. Gadi fageenya bakka ati jirtu agarsiisu qabadhu.
t_news_breaking_video::clip_card_4::goal: Yoo danda'ame, nama bakkchatti miidhameef gaaffiif deebii dhiyeessiif.
t_news_breaking_video::clip_card_6::goal: Bakkicha agarsiisi, bakka jirtu agarsiisuuf kofa haaraa fayyadami.
t_news_breaking_video::clip_card_5::goal: Oduun kun barbaachisaadha jettee sababa yaaddeef waan ibsu tokko qabadhu.
